---------------------------------------------


when we load .js into JS envi ,

browser will create 'global execution context'

 'window' <=== this
 
 all global var and functions will become properties of
 global-obj when in creation-phase
 with default value 'undefined'

-------------------------------------------
 
 
 JS - var hoisting is default featute i.1 lifting var dec to top
 
 every func invocation ,
 will create one new 'execution-context' which is child of existing
 
